data.description: This BRICK RANCH is just what you need:  CLOSE TO EVERYTHING with a CORNER LOT and OFF-STREET PARKING!  Recently RENOVATED in 2018, the interior of this home has 3 BEDROOMS and 1 BATHROOM featuring HARDWOOD and TILE flooring.   The exterior yard features plenty of room for gardening (on ALMOST 1/4 ACRE) and a pleasant BACK PATIO for relaxing or entertaining .   Less than 3 miles from GIANT, COSTCO, TARGET, and many popular dining places.
